\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"呢個只係球迷睇法<br />\n<br />\n拉膠的確受好多業內人士 名宿稱讚亦都係事實<br />\n<br />\n馬甸尼 安76 基亞連尼前幾年都讚過佢世一中堅<br />\n<br />\n19歲出道 一路穩佔正選至今<br />\n<br />\n西班牙、皇馬隊長 長期必然正選<br />\n<br />\n一定唔會係你講到咁差"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"單講技術都未必係<br />\n但計埋人品就真係唔好提佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好話咩單講技術點點點 <br />\nSorry 世一不嬲計埋球品"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T18:45:05.000Z","msg":"計球品就 朗同美斯都不合格"},{"pid":"23e70ea305b057deae3b3bdd2258fd1a70382547","tid":1136290,"uid":164874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T19:18:16.000Z","msg":"雲迪克先天身體體格條件好， 防守意識係好，步大力雄、靠身體質素去守波， 英超最佳係無錯。但我覺得佢有時企位麻麻，搞到隊友跟唔上，仲有上次對熱刺1vs2比人過份吹捧。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠狠勁， 熱血，頭頂鏟截最全面係拉莫斯，但今季表現最好係回勇嘅碧基。<br />\n始終個個聯賽要嘅中堅都有分別，只可以話大家都係頂級中堅。"},{"pid":"fe49b12200e54d3d33e9c84921deff56c92da9e3","tid":1136290,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T22:45:08.000Z","msg":"史魔寧，話要完封美斯講得出做得到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77961462fd3c5e382a00e031d76532f7d6a1609d","tid":1136290,"uid":29952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"887a7029c46b086f84261fb0caa7c50ca9ec64f5","tid":1136290,"uid":235465,"like":82,"dislike":15,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />VVD<br />\n無必要一場定生死 加埋比人長期榨乾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T00:34:01.000Z","msg":"打多幾季出色波先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沙拿上季雞胸都世三啦"},{"pid":"af3446d24b991c006b930f966c87c45a47884f5a","tid":1136290,"uid":29952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5bb7ad168a356b42f7aef23969120263dc7fe7d","tid":1136290,"uid":14656,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"quote":{"p